value.title: Pompeo claims Trump foreign policy has made world safer, Americans' lives 'more secure'

value.title: Former Pence aide says staffers discussed Trumps potential refusal to leave the White House

value.title: Joe Biden: Amy Coney Barrett is a threat to Obamacare

value.title: Did Kamala Harris’ family move to Jamaica to engage in the slave trade? No
value.excerpt: The elder Harris did write that his paternal grandmother descended from a slave owner. That part of his essay has been distorted repeatedly to fuel misleading claims on social media about the Harris family’s connections to slavery in Jamaica.

value.title: Biden says Senate should not act on Amy Coney Barrett Supreme Court nomination until after election
value.excerpt: Democratic presidential nominee Joe Biden on Saturday said the Senate should not act on Judge Amy Coney Barrett’s nomination to the Supreme Court until after “the American people select their next president and the next Congress.”

value.excerpt: It's no secret that Donald Trump is no big fan of the European Union. Over the past four years, the US President has talked positively about Brexit and claimed that the bloc was created in order to "take advantage of the United States."

value.title: Trump's work for Black community 'unparalleled to any other president' of past 50 years: Dem lawmaker
value.excerpt: President Trump's commitment to the African-American community is "unparalleled to any other president, Democrat or Republican, in the past 50 years," Georgia Democratic lawmaker Vernon Jones told "Special Report" Friday.

value.title: Bloomberg rolls out $40M ad buy to boost Biden in Florida
value.excerpt: Former New York City Mayor Michael Bloomberg on Friday rolled out a new $40 million ad buy in Florida as Democrats look to bolster Joe Biden’s chances of winning the Sunshine State.

value.title: The 2020 Election Collection: Claims About Mike Pence
